Hi guys! Today is January 20, 2020 

I made this map for fun, as I always wanted to do something nonstandard and I did it.

Try to go through all 56 levels on the map, which are not so difficult, the basis of the map includes 53 levels, 2 levels in the bonus (which are at the end of the map) and 1 solo level (which is in the center of the map).

Also at the end of the map you can buy a teleportation cannon from the portal, which is attached to the scout, and it is located behind your back (everyone sees it, it will not prevent you from passing the map in any way)

The map was developed a long time ago, yesterday I decided to play it with the players and everyone was quite happy, I just fixed the triggers a bit and I think that there shouldn’t be any problems, but if there are any problems with the map, then hurry up to inform me of them.

Compiled in HDR FULL COMPILE, also Added all the textures.

Sound Music Start, Russified voice acting at levels.

Thank you, good luck!

Ok. Me and my firend Colors where playing DeathRun for a few days ago and we thought it was pretty fun. So we created our own edit of DeathRun called ExplosiveRun

Ok im sure you wonder how you play it. here it is

Everyone starts at the same spawn without any gun. NOT EVEN A KNIFE. They have to jump over explosive barrels that have a detonator that will detonate them in 20 sec. If they survive they will enter a few corridors. Each corridor sets in to flames every 3rd sec so you have to be fast. And its some breakable floors to that you can get traped in and burn to death.
After the corridors you have to be first up to a wagon that contaions one and only one ak47. The guy who gets it will be able to shoot everybody else to death and if he dont the whole map will be set into flames in 20 sec and everyone will die.

It's really funny. I didnt thought that it was that fun untill i played it. I laghed all the time. Its perfect to play with your mates or have on your server.

I think we are the first who does this kind of map so therefore its no other category then DEATHRUN to post this in and im sorry for that.

It's recommended to use NOBLOCK when your playing this. Otherwise you wont be able to take the lead when you at last. And if you dont use noblock you might be blocked and die.!!

visit our webpage at http://www.zfh.cs.nu

Hey.

This map was created from scratch solely by Corn Ibulus. Questions / concerns go to him (me.)

This map's idea was based off Icepick's (Icepick66) Death_Run.

This FPSB account is thanks to Newborn King (or ingame †ÎK† Ñėẅbörn K¡ng{MG}.)

Overview: The terrorists are locked in a building suspended over a large pit. Their only weapons are knives and buttons, which correspond to traps outside the building.

Objective: TERRORISTS - The counter-terrorists are out to get you, and your only defense is a series of traps designed to kill anyone and everyone. You will need to work together to the best extent choosing who works what obstacle at what time. If you fail, and a counter terrorist makes it to the top, you will have to scramble and form an alliance to take down the monster with a shotgun using only knives and strategy.

COUNTER TERRORISTS - Those pesky terrorists are keeping you from the shotgun at the top of the looming building. You will need to dodge traps using your l33t ninja skills you claim to have. If you prove yourself worthy and an adept runner, you will be granted a shotgun, which you will then use to take down the terrorists. However, make your shots count, because it will be embarrasing if a terrorist lands a blow on you with a knife...

Gameplay: Out of all the death_run remixes, this one is the HARDEST so far, depending on the skills of the terrorists. Don't expect the shotgun to be an easy grab, unless the terrorists are completely clueless. AFK's are not a problem, they will all be killed in at least a minute. The run is TIMED, from the moment a terrorist touches the floor. Here's the timer system overview: after 60 seconds the CT spawn is destroyed (taking afk's with it.) Then, every 5 seconds a stretch of the floor breaks, and the trap on that floor malfunctions and goes out of control.

Thanks to all who helped me along with this map. Also thanks to Icepick for the amazing idea. I hope everyone enjoys this map as much as me and my friends do.

The map takes place in a classroom where the CT's spawn. They proceed through some dangerous traps on the hallways and next on the courtyard. The map has nice textures with good lightning.

The map contains of 30 CT spawns and 2 T spawns, 3 secret grenade spots and around 17 traps without breaking floors...

At the end, you can pick Bunny hop and Easy. Didn't make "knife" since you can have a knife fight on easy if wanted.

The map should work without any problems, but still I named it V2 and not "final" for any other player complainments. If there is anything wrong with the download or anything else, please do not flag but rather comment. :)

To install the map, simply put the cstrike folder contained in the download over the old one in you counter strike folder.

Commenting and rating is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D

Hey this is a deathrun map I made. It contains 15 traps and a few traps i havent seen in any other dr map. Though I havent seen every dr map.

The second trap can only be passed by throwing a nade through a small hole in the wall.

The barnacles have animations and sound.

The HL2 Dog trap has animations and sounds. Its player controlled and throws barrels. It has to be knifed to death to pass. You cant use the dog trap button if theres more than one person near it, i had it lock because if 2 people get in the trap it will crash your server when it dies.

The rest of the things I'll let you discover since I dont want to bore you with a long essay. Check out the screenshots they should help you get somewhat of a grasp of the map. I didnt use any prefabs in the map other than for the letters. I dont mind if you decompile the map to see how i made a trap (the barnacles were tricky) but if you're gonna use anything let me know. If you find any glitches/bugs in the map also let me know. The map may be constructed sort of weird, with the walls, but my clan's server has rpg mod and i needed to stop people from bhopping thru all the traps.

Version b3 is out as of 11 PM Pacific on July 3, 2008.

Numerous improvements have been made, most notably the map's appearance.

Not-so-detailed changelog
-----------------------------
b3)
-The entire map now has a haunted house theme
-Very improved lighting
-"CREDITS" text no longer casts shadows
-Changed first trap's walls to boxes
-Replaced bullseye targets with laser targeting
-Changed the grenade trap to have crates and lowered the starting position to make the trap deadlier
-Added more to the sliderace's wall, so terrorists can't time the sliderace trap to kill you as you pass
-Increased the size of the lightning trap
-Fixed the exploit that allowed players to get weapons from the end of the map
-Added free pointless weapons on top of the crate
-Fixed a slight spacing problem with the spikes on the stairs
-Removed the helicopter
-Tightened the hallways of the 2nd floor to be equal with the 1st floor
-Changed the appearance of the teleporter trap
-Changed the turret trap's doors from glass to match the sliderace's...it's going back to something transparent for b4
-Added a few more nails on the hammer trap
-Changed how the final trap spins to force the player being knocked off the platform
-Made the glass wall near the T stairs break sooner
-Changed the buttons to much nicer-looking ones, although they still lack an on/off light
-Made slight visual changes to the fire and gas fun box buttons
